    "en": {
      "name": "Assault Blackwing - Kusanagi the Gathering Storm",
      "effect": "1 Tuner + 1+ non-Tuners\nIf this card is Synchro Summoned using a \"Blackwing\" monster as material, it is treated as a Tuner while face-up on the field. After this card is Synchro Summoned, for the rest of this turn, it gains ATK equal to the total original ATK of the Synchro Monsters used as its material. Can attack all your opponent's monsters, once each. If this card attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage to your opponent.",
      "official": false
    },
